item.title: WNBA Expansion Team Golden State Valkyries Unveil Name, Logo
item.description: Franchise name references warrior women from Norse mythology; logo depicts Bay Bridge between Oakland, where they'll train, and San Francisco, where they'll play home games

item.title: New York Giants Unveil 100th Season Logo, Uniform Patch
item.description: The New York Giants kicked off their 100th season celebration on Monday morning by unveiling a commemorative logo, which will be worn as a patch on their uniforms this fall.
